```console
$ cargo-samply samply --samply-args="--rate 2000" --dry-run
cargo build '--message-format=json-diagnostic-rendered-ansi' --profile samply --bin samply-args
[..]record --rate 2000 -- [..]target[..]samply[..]samply-args[..]

```

```console
$ cargo-samply samply --samply-args="--rate 2000 --save-only profile.json" --dry-run
cargo build '--message-format=json-diagnostic-rendered-ansi' --profile samply --bin samply-args
[..]record --rate 2000 --save-only profile.json -- [..]target[..]samply[..]samply-args[..]

```

